ivardefs.name: adjudication_
ivardefs.desc: If this item is a group then the values here are a summary of the adjudication of the detail items. If this item is a simple product or service then this is the result of the adjudication of this item.

ivardefs.name: detail_
ivardefs.desc: A claim detail. Either a simple (a product or service) or a 'group' of sub-details which are simple items.

ivardefs.name: itemSequence
ivardefs.desc: A number to uniquely reference the claim item entries.

ivardefs.name: noteNumber_
ivardefs.desc: The numbers associated with notes below which apply to the adjudication of this item.

properties.desc: A claim line. Either a simple (a product or service) or a 'group' of details which can also be a simple items or groups of sub-details.
